{
  "stem": "24885.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The other places of worship were not so affected because they were small.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I think I mentioned to you the place that we used to go to was the rabbi's house.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They only accommodated maybe 30 or 40 people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So they just closed up and that was it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "There was no place to go to daven during the ghetto an so on.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And if there was, you didn't take a chance.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "You were afraid that somebody will turn on you or whatever.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "There was always somebody against it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were able to get out-- we had rations, first of all, ration cards or whatever.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we were able to go out, as I explained to you, like I used to go out with covering up.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my mother-- it was easier for a woman to get out of the ghetto than a man, and a mother was able to go to the farmers or to people she has known and pick up food.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A woman they didn't bother so much as a man, for some reason.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know why.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh yeah, you had to hide it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were regular dressed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We didn't have prison garb yet.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Regular clothes, but we had the armband.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Was supposed to wear it up here, but you slid it down here and wore a coat over it.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then we had to go out to work.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was a Star of David with the word Jude on it, just like in my passport there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not-- when I went to work, I didn't.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When I went to work for them, I think I mentioned we all had to go out to work.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
